---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Directory Website Redesign Service | Stackbase System" description="Redesign outdated directory websites into fast, SEO-ready, conversion-focused platforms with cleaner architecture.">
  <section class="pt-24 pb-14">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <span class="text-sm text-[#00f0ff] font-['JetBrains_Mono'] tracking-wider">DIRECTORY REDESIGN</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mt-4 mb-5 font-['Space_Grotesk']">Directory website redesign for teams outgrowing slow, messy stacks</h1>
      <p class="text-[#8b8b9a] text-lg max-w-3xl">If your current directory feels outdated, slow, or difficult to maintain, this service replaces fragile structure with modern UX, clean architecture, and technical SEO foundations built for long-term growth.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-10">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] mb-4">What redesign usually fixes</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-[#c7c7d2]"><li>• Slow loading pages and weak mobile performance</li><li>• Broken IA and confusing user journeys</li><li>• Template inconsistency across listing/location pages</li><li>• Technical SEO gaps hurting indexation and trust</li><li>• Hard-to-maintain plugin dependencies</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] mb-4">What changes after rebuild</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-[#c7c7d2]"><li>• Sharper visual hierarchy and premium first impression</li><li>• Better listing discovery with cleaner filters/search UX</li><li>• More stable, maintainable codebase</li><li>• SEO technical baseline aligned with growth</li><li>• A site you can confidently present to partners and buyers</li></ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-10">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-white font-['Space_Grotesk'] mb-4">Good redesign candidates</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-[#c7c7d2]"><p>• WordPress directories with plugin and performance issues</p><p>• Legacy builds with no clear SEO architecture</p><p>• Sites with declining conversion despite steady traffic</p><p>• Teams preparing for investor/client-facing relaunch</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-14">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="/pricing" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-[#0a0a0f] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#00f0ff] to-[#00c8ff] rounded-xl">See redesign scope options</a>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl">Send your current site URL</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
